EmailTemplate.subject: Your invited to the screening of the Oak Bay - LIve Different Build highlight video!
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Join the Volunteers from Oak Bay for an evening of celebration!
7 pm on the evening of May 24th Dave Dunnet Theatre Oak Bay High School
Hello,
As many of you have already heard, Live Different Oak Bay 2018 was an astounding success! The students worked extremely hard throughout the fourteen months leading up to the trip and I couldn't be any prouder of their dedication and commitment once we arrived in Mexico. It's amazing to see the confidence, awareness, and maturity that develops in such a short period of time. None of this would have been possible without your assistance. As a thank you, we hope that you can join us at 7 pm on the evening of May 24 in the Oak Bay High School Dave Dunnet Theatre. We will be presenting a 40 minute video highlighting our journey. This night also allows friends, families, and donors to witness firsthand how this adventure has affected the students.
We really hope you are able to share this memorable night with us.
Thank you again for all that you do,
Brent and Nichelle Garraway
Live Different Suite 111 - 1429 Main St East, Hamilton, ON L8K 1C2 (866) 432 4464
